{"tid":2196333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅：香港事務是中國內政　東亞峰會不是攻擊別國舞台","createTime":"2020-09-09T22:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T04:02:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":181,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"745723a9fb0c5cc5f98ee4adcdf48eac2c21f8e0","tid":2196333,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T22:13:23.000Z","msg":"國務委員兼外長王毅重申，香港事務是中國內政，不干涉內政是國際關係基本準則，也是聯合國憲章的重要規定，各國都有義務遵守。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，針對美國等個別國家在第十屆東亞峰會外長會議上就涉港問題說三道四，王毅指出，東亞峰會是領導人引領的戰略論壇，從來不是介入別國內政的場所，更不應成為攻擊他國政治制度的舞台。<br />\n<br />\n王毅說，一國的政治法律制度到底好不好，這個國家的公民最有發言權，而不是別國的政府或甚麼政客。所有國際民調結果都顯示，中國人民對中國執政黨和中國政府的支持度都高居全球榜首。這一事實是對那些抹黑攻擊中國勢力的最有力回擊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548782-20200910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548782-20200910.htm&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=edd2ece6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548782-20200910.htm&h=f1d2feb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548782-20200910.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e5583d68532db47f2bfeeb8ab0d0e318af033213","tid":2196333,"uid":51701,"like":149,"dislike":0,"score":149,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T22:14:28.000Z","msg":"驚？Quit囉"},{"pid":"c946b60503b0901e8180a14930f8524ead44f01b","tid":2196333,"uid":312363,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T22:16:18.000Z","msg":"發言權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c8162bbc9b5577943657d8265a4c1999aaf270","tid":2196333,"uid":278533,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T22:24:58.000Z","msg":"呢斑人唔好咁痴線啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7249e3af9935ba672948ed7c1f3dd14e97b71e","tid":2196333,"uid":20641,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T22:34:58.000Z